description:
Lance Hart just moved to Las Vegas from LA. He thinks he found a sweet deal on rent in a place owned by Charlotte Sartre. When going over the lease he notices a clause that states that he’ll be fucked in the ass twice a day…

Charlotte assures him that it’s a Clark County HOA standard thing… So Lance shrugs and goes with it.

Then she fucks his ass and clearly enjoys it.
title: Cheap Rent with Charlotte Sartre
